OL,3,CSteve Jack revealed as ITV Border
OL,4,Cfundraiser of the year for 2025
OL,6,FDumfries and Galloway's Steve Jack has
OL,7,Fbeen revealed as ITV Border's
OL,8,Ffundraiser of the year for 2025.
OL,10,FSteve Jack, from Eastriggs near
OL,11,FGretna, raised thousands for local
OL,12,Fchildren through physical challenges.
OL,14,FBorn with spina bifida, Steve has been
OL,15,Fin a wheelchair since birth. In 2009,
OL,16,Fan infection that led to sepsis meant
OL,17,Fhe had to have one leg amputated to
OL,18,Fsave his life.
