OL,6,FThree years later, he came into
OL,7,Fhospital for a routine operation and
OL,8,Fsuffered a major bleed.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV Border's weather
OL,11,Fpresenter Ross Hutchinson, Steve Jack
OL,12,Fsaid: "I am just glad that I have
OL,13,Fhelped people. It is just something I
OL,14,Fwant to do.
OL,16,F"I can't give anything back to the
OL,17,Fdoctors and nurses who saved me, so if
OL,18,FI can help someone else then I will
OL,19,Fdo."
