OL,3,CSteve Jack revealed as ITV Border
OL,4,Cfundraiser of the year for 2025
OL,6,FWhen in rehab from his operation,
OL,7,FSteve heard about a local boy named
OL,8,FJoshua who needed specialist equipment
OL,9,Fto help live with cerebral palsy.
OL,11,FSteve set his sights on the fells,
OL,12,Fclimbing to the top of Latrigg above
OL,13,FKeswick, raising #2000 to help Joshua
OL,14,Ftowards a more active childhood.
OL,16,FJoshua told us: "I am incredibly
OL,17,Fgrateful for Steve for wanting to help
OL,18,Fme, even though we had never even met.
OL,19,FThe money Steve raised went towards an
OL,20,Foff-road wheelchair which has changed
OL,21,Fmy life.
