OL,6,F"I can now go places like across the
OL,7,Fpark, along the beach and in the woods
OL,8,Findependently and enjoy the outdoors
OL,9,Fwith my friends."
OL,11,FEarlier this year, Steve heard about
OL,12,Fanother local child, three-year-old
OL,13,FKoda being treated for Leukaemia.
OL,15,FOnce again, Steve hit the gym with a
OL,16,Fgoal in mind, becoming the first
OL,17,Fwheelchair user to complete the Cross
OL,18,FBorder 10K race, raising more than
OL,19,F#2800 for Koda's family.
